{"tid":307181,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日踩15小時　司機猝死","createTime":"2017-07-03T07:09:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-03T08:17:01.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"975b6bffe4e5ed498eab7e8d8eb44b3120c2d4e0","tid":307181,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T07:09:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170703/20077066\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170703%2F20077066&d=cIbmEudI4lsiCKtkGVUrqv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=bded752a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170703%2F20077066&h=bc86c236\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170703/20077066</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日踩15小時　司機猝死<br />\n<br />\n10,027<br />\n ■李添帶送院後證實不治。溫瑞麟攝<br />\n適中字型<br />\n較大字型<br />\n■李添帶送院後證實不治。溫瑞麟攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】49歲的士司機近日抱病開工，上周五致電妻子稱不適後失聯，家人報警求助。前晚姨甥在西環尋獲事主的士，發現他昏迷車內，送院證實不治，遺下妻女、母親及患病兄長。<br />\n遺下妻子及兩歲女<br />\n死者李添帶在內地娶妻，於羅湖租屋住，有一名兩歲大女兒，妻子偶爾持雙程證來港。另外，李要供養母親及長期患病的兄長，故返特長更（朝9晚12），每月工作25日，收工後返羅湖。<br />\n上周五晚上8時許，李開工時致電身在羅湖的妻子，稱感不適，要停在路邊休息。未幾，李妻致電丈夫但無人接聽，向親友求助後報警。<br />\n事主姨甥認識事主同業朋友，其中一名的士司機載他尋人，至前晚8時許，在西環皇后大道西513號對開路邊發現事主的士，見他昏迷車內遂報警，終證實不治，其妻帶同女兒到醫院認屍。<br />\n警方發現的士開着引擎，車上有麵包、一樽水及一盒藥，不排除他開工時病發猝死，但真正原因仍待確定。<br />\n■記者曾海帆<br />\n<br />\n97年主權移交至今，香港前進還是倒退？「蘋果」與你細數廿載風雨。<br />\n【回歸二十年】專頁：<a href=\"http://hksar20.appledaily.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhksar20.appledaily.com.hk&d=cIbmEudI4lsiCKtkGVUrqv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=baaa5cf9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hksar20.appledaily.com.hk</a>  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n足球名宿留醫12小時不治<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n游水失蹤　車長未尋回"},{"pid":"5efb837a02c4f2dcb54612e4103ada5d55975e85","tid":307181,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T07:12:18.000Z","msg":"窮人死幾多都唔會有人重視<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2828e8b7afe244440345ef2982a9b291529f863","tid":307181,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T07:19:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>窮人死幾多都唔會有人重視<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n重要學人生下一代 無撚腦"},{"pid":"e6b14f29f092f8214ba0de475304073fe58397d9","tid":307181,"uid":104088,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T07:20:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4946b8fd59a7cdb372f02baae121978346634600","tid":307181,"uid":81569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T07:23:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>窮人死幾多都唔會有人重視<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢位司機算係咁啦<br />\n係大陸住，又自力更生"},{"pid":"8b492828da844101d4f2e0834dc3435501cc1027","tid":307181,"uid":13828,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T07:25:43.000Z","msg":"乜撚野失聯？失蹤就失蹤啦！毒果正一賣港報"},{"pid":"c761875aa74db7498cc95d6c8d9f32a2009795f4","tid":307181,"uid":118120,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T07:26:10.000Z","msg":"窮人生仔 = 玩死自己<br />\n<br />\n唔生仔單身既話都叫可以自給自足<br />\n<br />\n生仔既話唔過勞死就係抑鬱到自殺, 好多case都係咁"},{"pid":"c57d8343b43b5a8ad811848d3e07eea1b22f6bd0","tid":307181,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T07:38:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9284bf0c017dee78136c90598545bfe77196d611","tid":307181,"uid":51343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T07:47:12.000Z","msg":"在內地娶妻"},{"pid":"49cc9fa49fb4577f4e54e03c8190f0e3fe442383","tid":307181,"uid":76171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T07:47:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>福氣來架👍，一諗到係香港死做爛做買唔到一層300呎樓，一份人工養唔起冚家😅，喂！福氣來架👍<br />\n<br />\n港喱廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/10/180317_03cbd1af556a332f8883b810f17ea9e5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-sr